# 10. Validation Philosophy

PANDA shall be validated using published experimental detector-response measurements before being used to predict SEE cross sections.

Validation hierarchy:

1. Alpha particles

2. Proton energy deposition

3. Neutron detector response

4. Proton SEE

5. Neutron SEE

